public class PartDescriptorImpl extends ApplicationElementImpl implements MPartDescriptor
An implementation of the model object 'Part Descriptor'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Label
  • Icon URI
  • Tooltip
  • Localized Label
  • Localized Tooltip
  • Handlers
  • Binding Contexts
  • Allow Multiple
  • Category
  • Menus
  • Toolbar
  • Closeable
